      "id": "l01-greetings",
      "title": "Greetings & politeness",
      "intro": "## How greetings work in Spanish\n\nSpanish greetings follow the time of day: **buenos días** until midday, **buenas tardes** through the afternoon and early evening, **buenas noches** after dark (both as a greeting and a farewell).\n\nNote the pattern: *buenos/buenas* agrees with the noun — **días** is masculine (buen**os**), **tardes** and **noches** are feminine (buen**as**).\n\n**Hola** works any time, and politeness words (**por favor**, **gracias**, **de nada**) are used far more freely than their English counterparts — sprinkle them generously.",
      "cards": [
        { "id": "hola", "front": "hola", "back": "hello", "tts": "hola", "reverse": true,
          "example": { "text": "¡Hola! ¿Qué tal?", "translation": "Hello! How's it going?" } },
        { "id": "buenos-dias", "front": "buenos días", "back": "good morning", "tts": "buenos días", "reverse": true,
          "example": { "text": "Buenos días, señora.", "translation": "Good morning, ma'am." } },
        { "id": "buenas-tardes", "front": "buenas tardes", "back": "good afternoon", "tts": "buenas tardes", "reverse": true,
          "example": { "text": "Buenas tardes a todos.", "translation": "Good afternoon, everyone." } },
        { "id": "buenas-noches", "front": "buenas noches", "back": "good evening / good night", "tts": "buenas noches", "reverse": true,
          "example": { "text": "Buenas noches, hasta mañana.", "translation": "Good night, see you tomorrow." } },
        { "id": "adios", "front": "adiós", "back": "goodbye", "tts": "adiós", "reverse": true,
          "example": { "text": "Adiós, nos vemos pronto.", "translation": "Goodbye, see you soon." } },
        { "id": "por-favor", "front": "por favor", "back": "please", "tts": "por favor", "reverse": true,
          "example": { "text": "Un café, por favor.", "translation": "A coffee, please." } },
        { "id": "gracias", "front": "gracias", "back": "thank you", "tts": "gracias", "reverse": true,
          "example": { "text": "Muchas gracias por tu ayuda.", "translation": "Thank you very much for your help." } },
        { "id": "de-nada", "front": "de nada", "back": "you're welcome", "tts": "de nada", "reverse": true,
          "example": { "text": "—Gracias. —De nada.", "translation": "—Thanks. —You're welcome." } }
      ]
    },
